        <li class="hidden">Go to developer options , then turn on <strong>usb debugging</strong> and also turn on <strong>Disable Permission Monitoring</strong> <em>if it exists</em>.</li>
        <li class="hidden">Connect your phone to the Windows pc using an usb cable.</li>
        <li class="hidden">Download and extract the file <a href="https://github.com/legendsayantan/ThemePatcher/releases/latest">ThemePatcher.zip</a>.</li>
        <li class="hidden">Open Theme Store in the android device, choose whatever paid themes you like and click <strong>Free trial</strong>.</li>
        <li class="hidden">Run the file <strong>ThemePatcher.bat</strong> in the extracted folder.</li>
        <li class="hidden">Trials from Theme store will not expire anymore even after the demo runs out!</li>
    </ol>
    <br />
    <h4 id="lin">Linux</h4>
    <ol dir="auto">
        <li class="hidden">Tap on the build number <strong>seven times</strong> in your android device to enable developer options.</li>
        <li class="hidden">Go to developer options , then turn on <strong>usb debugging</strong> and also turn on <strong>Disable Permission Monitoring</strong> <em>if it exists</em>.</li>
