        <li class="hidden">Go to developer options , then turn on <strong>usb debugging</strong> and also turn on <strong>Disable Permission Monitoring</strong> <em>if it exists</em>.</li>
        <li class="hidden">Connect your phone to the Mac using an usb cable.</li>
        <li class="hidden">Install brew using <code>/bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install.sh)"</code>.</li>
        <li class="hidden">Install adb using <code>brew install android-platform-tools</code></li>
        <li class="hidden">Download the file <a href="https://github.com/legendsayantan/ThemePatcher/releases/latest">ThemePatcher.sh</a>.</li>
        <li class="hidden">Enable execution of the script using <code>chmod +x ThemePatcher.sh</code>.</li>
